Ever wondered what the secret to starting a business with a close friend is? Ego Iwegbu, Azania Mosaka and Linda Jangulo, the co-owners of the Miss Salon London boutique beauty bars and MSLondon Mineral Cosmetics, let us in on it Ego Iwegbu, Azania Mosaka and Linda Jangulo own three booming nail and beauty salons in Johannesburg and Pretoria, as well as a cult make-up brand. The trio have mastered the art of going into business as friends. The secret, they say, is that they always put their businesses first. “We keep it professional, even though we are friends,” says Jangulo. Watch video below: